OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772503387
OL,3,CVideo shows US fighter jets shot down
OL,4,Cin 'apparent friendly fire incident'
OL,6,FThree American fighter jets were
OL,7,F"mistakenly shot down" by friendly
OL,8,FKuwait fire during an Iranian air
OL,9,Fassault, the US military said on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,FFootage posted online shows a jet
OL,13,Ffalling from the sky in flames and a
OL,14,Fpilot parachuting to the ground. The
OL,15,Fvideo appeared to show an F-15E
OL,16,Ffighter jet, according to ITV News'
OL,17,Fpartner CNN's analysis.
OL,19,FThe incident occurred as Iranian
OL,20,Faircraft, missiles, and drones carried
OL,21,Fout attacks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772503387
OL,3,CVideo shows US fighter jets shot down
OL,4,Cin 'apparent friendly fire incident'
OL,6,FAll six crew members safely ejected
OL,7,Ffrom the F-15E Strike Eagles and were
OL,8,Fin stable condition after being
OL,9,Frecovered, the US said in a statement,
OL,10,Fwhich you can read in full here.
OL,12,FKuwait said its air defences
OL,13,Faccidentally shot down the jets as
OL,14,Fpart of its support for the US combat
OL,15,Foperation in Iran, US Central Command
OL,16,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,18,FIt said: "Three US F-15E Strike Eagles
OL,19,Fflying in support of Operation Epic
OL,20,FFury went down over Kuwait due to an
OL,21,Fapparent friendly fire incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772503387
OL,3,CVideo shows US fighter jets shot down
OL,4,Cin 'apparent friendly fire incident'
OL,6,F"Kuwait has acknowledged this
OL,7,Fincident, and we are grateful for the
OL,8,Fefforts of the Kuwaiti defense forces
OL,9,Fand their support in this ongoing
OL,10,Foperation."
OL,12,FThe cause of the incident was under
OL,13,Finvestigation, the US said.
OL,15,FIranian state television had also
OL,16,Fclaimed that Iran had targeted one of
OL,17,Fthe US aircraft that crashed in
OL,18,FKuwait. It did not elaborate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
