PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772503387
OL,3,CVideo shows US fighter jets shot down
OL,4,Cin 'apparent friendly fire incident'
OL,6,FExplosions could be heard as one of
OL,7,Fthe planes fell from the sky in
OL,8,Fflames, witness Ahmed al-Asar told the
OL,9,FAssociated Press, who rushed to the
OL,10,Fscene with about a dozen others as an
OL,11,Fairman parachuted to the ground.
OL,13,FAl-Asar initially thought it was an
OL,14,FIranian pilot, but recognised he was
OL,15,FAmerican before rescuers whisked him
OL,16,Faway.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
