OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772503387
OL,3,CVideo shows US fighter jets shot down
OL,4,Cin 'apparent friendly fire incident'
OL,6,FOn Saturday, the US and Israel
OL,7,Flaunched "major combat operations" in
OL,8,FIran, which led to the death of the
OL,9,FIranian Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali
OL,10,FKhamenei.
OL,12,FIran has since vowed to retaliate with
OL,13,F"devastating blows" and fired missiles
OL,14,Fat many of its neighbouring countries
OL,15,Fas well as US military targets.
OL,17,FAt least 555 people in Iran have been
OL,18,Fkilled since US-Israeli airstrikes
OL,19,Fbegan targeting the country over the
OL,20,Fweekend, the Iranian Red Crescent
OL,21,FSociety said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
