OL,3,CVideo shows US fighter jets shot down
OL,4,Cin 'apparent friendly fire incident'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Israeli airstrikes on
OL,7,FBeirut and southern Lebanon on Monday
OL,8,Fkilled at least 31 people and injured
OL,9,F149, according to Lebanon's health
OL,10,Fministry.
OL,12,FUS Central Command also said the death
OL,13,Ftoll of American service members has
OL,14,Frisen to four after one person, who
OL,15,Fwas "seriously injured during Iran's
OL,16,Finitial attacks, eventually succumbed
OL,17,Fto their injuries."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
